#: data/civ1/buildings.ruleset:641 data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:893
#: data/civ2civ3/buildings.ruleset:1072 data/classic/buildings.ruleset:933
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:992
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:910 data/royale/buildings.ruleset:1166
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:1057
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Space Components can be differentiated into Propulsion and Fuel Components. "
